{"tid":1587450,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"林鄭出席工聯會活動 強調會止暴制亂保障工友飯碗","createTime":"2019-09-22T11:45:26.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-22T15:19:58.000Z","uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":5,"replies":[{"pid":"21646e435e9807fff5079793e4d06086df7991f5","tid":1587450,"uid":133680,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-22T11:45:26.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2601452003251284/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2F420361564693683%2Fposts%2F2601452003251284%2F&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=99e201e9\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/420361564693683/posts/2601452003251284/</a><br />\n<br />\n【林鄭出席工聯會活動 強調會止暴制亂保障工友飯碗】<br />\n<br />\n特首林鄭月娥今午（9月22日）出席工聯會慶祝中華人民共和國成立70周年的酒會，指在過去一段時間香港社會面對極大挑戰，特區政府一定會竭盡全力止暴制亂，維持社會的秩序，保障工友飯碗。<br />\n<br />\n林鄭表示，香港的工友一向都有「獅子山」的精神，認為只要大家團結一致，自強不息，相信在北京的大力支持下，香港一定會迎來更美好的明天。<br />\n<br />\n全文︰<a href=\"http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-22-2019/56124\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.passiontimes.hk%2Farticle%2F09-22-2019%2F56124&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=33a083cb\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.passiontimes.hk/article/09-22-2019/56124</a><br />\n<br />\n#林鄭月娥 #工聯會<br />\n<br />\n請支持PassionPrime：<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/prime/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2Fprime%2F&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=72d38d3e\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/prime/</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血時報印刷版︰<br />\n<a href=\"http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fpassiontimes.hk%2F4.0%2Fregform.php&d=AaXh75k8ef15jyN5JBlvBvQJlsOaju8aQhUrU01WOmc%3D&h=50183c37\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://passiontimes.hk/4.0/regform.php</a><br />\n<br />\n請支持熱血文青課金計劃：<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.passiontime